			<div class="content" id="post-content-1137849">
									

<p>Re: your question, I don't see the entity as being contained by solely physical means. It's entirely possible to open the door and walk in without it escaping, but doing so without proper preparation is like walking into 173's containment without being told about the whole &quot;keep your eyes on it&quot; bit. Possible, but unwise and unhealthy.</p>
<p>That said, I may write up some excerpts of translated inscriptions to add clarity, but I'll probably put them in either a collapsible block or a separate document, as this article is getting dangerously wall-of-text already.</p>

							</div>

								
					
